import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button";
import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";
import React from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";

function AddAccount() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Form>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextAccountClassification"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Account Classification
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm="10">
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Asset" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextAccountType"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Account Type
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm="10">
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Asset" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextAccountParent"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Account Parent
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm="10">
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextAcountNumber"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Account Number
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm="1">
            <Form.Control placeholder="1 -" />
          </Col>
          <Col sm="9">
            <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextAccountName"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Account Name
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm="10">
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group
          as={Row}
          className="mb-3"
          controlId="formPlaintextOpeningBalance"
        >
          <Form.Label column sm="2">
            Opening Balance
          </Form.Label>

          <Col sm="10">
            <Form.Label>Rp.</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="Number" placeholder="" />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
      </Form>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default AddAccount;
